04:15.233 --> 04:16.767
I picked her up,
I gave her, like, a big hug."

04:16.767 --> 04:18.433
Hello.
- Hi.

04:18.433 --> 04:21.066
- [grunts]
- [groans]

04:21.066 --> 04:23.367
