forever.

08:57.166 --> 08:59.533
- Mm-hmm.
- So I would concentrate

08:59.533 --> 09:01.734
on being the girlfriend.

09:01.734 --> 09:04.000
- Yes.
- But the question is,

09:04.000 --> 09:05.467
