she's screwed,

10:31.000 --> 10:32.500
and it goes to court,
and it's like a legal thing,

10:32.500 --> 10:33.734
and blah-blah-blah.

10:33.734 --> 10:34.767
I'm just--it makes me nervous

10:34.767 --> 10:36.333
