10:36.333 --> 10:39.133
- I haven't seen her
since Austen's beer event.

10:39.133 --> 10:40.600
- First of all,
I loved the beer.

10:40.600 --> 10:42.233
- I did too.
- I am so proud of him.

10:42.233 --> 10:44.333
