Do you know that?

34:08.600 --> 34:10.133
- Good.
Let's leave it that way.

34:11.467 --> 34:13.200
- Yeah, definitely
don't want Ashley to know.

34:15.200 --> 34:17.066
- All right, love you too, bud.
We'll see you soon.

