- Hey, how are y'all?
- Hey.

34:32.300 --> 34:34.600
Table for two, please.

34:34.600 --> 34:37.166
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

34:37.166 --> 34:38.166
Y'all enjoy.

34:38.166 --> 34:39.200
- [sighs]

34:39.200 --> 34:41.600
- Voila.

34:41.600 --> 34:43.734
- [soft cough]
- How about a bottle of wine?

34:43.734 --> 34:45.633
- I'd love that.

34:45.633 --> 34:47.500
That and a cough drop.

34:47.500 --> 34:50.734
- [clinking glass]
- Thomas--stop.

34:50.734 --> 34:53.233
- What? I'm trying to
get us some service.

34:53.233 --> 34:54.500
[sighs]

34:54.500 --> 34:55.633
- Hello, good evening, folks.

34:55.633 --> 34:57.100
How are you?
- How you doing?

34:57.100 --> 34:58.700
How about this bottle
from Portugal?

34:58.700 --> 35:01.367
- Absolutely.
- The "Lobo."

35:01.367 --> 35:03.500
- Alrighty.
- I'll have "the wolf."

35:03.500 --> 35:05.567
They used to call me the wolf,
you know, when I was single.

35:05.567 --> 35:08.633
- It might not be long
until you're single again.

35:08.633 --> 35:11.233
- You gonna br--
you breaking up with me?

35:11.233 --> 35:15.300
You know, I've been
doing my best to make you mine.

35:15.300 --> 35:17.367
- You're not doing
a very good job at it.

35:17.367 --> 35:18.767
[pensive marimba music]

35:18.767 --> 35:20.367
I know that I love you,

35:20.367 --> 35:22.200
but I think we hit,
like, a little rough patch.

35:22.200 --> 35:25.667
Since I've been back,
it's been very volatile.

35:25.667 --> 35:27.400
Or I just feel like
you're just on edge.

35:27.400 --> 35:29.667
- Yeah, we were apart ten days.

35:29.667 --> 35:32.533
You know, it was like
I was picking up a stranger.

35:32.533 --> 35:35.133
I'm like, "Who is this person?"

35:35.133 --> 35:39.533
- I'm starting to really
assess everything.

35:39.533 --> 35:41.667
And there's a lot of red flags.

35:41.667 --> 35:44.133
The pros and the cons,
I look at them both and I think,

35:44.133 --> 35:46.667
"About even."

35:46.667 --> 35:50.533
- All right, sir,
the 1995 Poco Do Lobo Arinto.

35:50.533 --> 35:52.133
Portugal.

35:54.266 --> 35:56.133
- I like it.
- Drains pretty well, huh?

35:56.133 --> 35:58.133
- That's interesting tasting.

35:58.133 --> 35:59.767
- Folks, what can
I get for you this evening?

35:59.767 --> 36:01.533
- The fish special sounds good.
- Sound good.

36:01.533 --> 36:04.133
Thank you, sir.
- Appreciate it.

36:04.133 --> 36:07.266
Something keeps jabbing me
right here.

36:07.266 --> 36:10.266
Can I just go ahead
and give this to you?

36:11.567 --> 36:14.033
There you go.
That's for you.

36:14.033 --> 36:15.266
- [soft gasp]

36:15.266 --> 36:18.266
[softly]
Babe.

36:18.266 --> 36:20.033
- Go ahead.
- Thank you.

36:20.033 --> 36:21.300
I didn't expect you
to get me a present.

36:21.300 --> 36:22.567
- I think you'll be fond of it.

36:22.567 --> 36:24.633
It goes with
what you're wearing.

36:26.300 --> 36:28.533
[dramatic tone]

36:34.433 --> 36:36.166
[cymbal shimmers]

36:36.166 --> 36:38.400
- Barrel fish for you.
- Thank you so much.

36:38.400 --> 36:40.133
- Thank you.

36:40.133 --> 36:42.533
- Thank you so much.
- Absolutely.

36:42.533 --> 36:44.667
- How do we move forward?

36:44.667 --> 36:46.300
- I think a healthy relationship

36:46.300 --> 36:48.200
is interdependent;
it's not codependent.

36:48.200 --> 36:50.266
Sometimes I feel like
you get a little needy.

36:50.266 --> 36:51.700
[soft dramatic music]

36:51.700 --> 36:53.333
You're kind of lonely;

36:53.333 --> 36:55.033
you don't know many
people in Charleston.

36:55.033 --> 36:57.700
And that's put
a strain on our relationship.

36:57.700 --> 36:59.200
If I were clingy and needy,
you--

36:59.200 --> 37:01.033
would I be an attractive man
to you?

37:01.033 --> 37:04.567
I think you need to
get involved with something

37:04.567 --> 37:06.467
outside of me.

37:06.467 --> 37:09.300
- Okay. Like getting a job?
- Yeah.

37:09.300 --> 37:11.467
- As soon as I can get
my nursing license, yes.

37:11.467 --> 37:13.700
- You know, you're looking to me

37:13.700 --> 37:15.433
to be your tower of strength,

37:15.433 --> 37:18.200
when you need to
find it within yourself.

37:18.200 --> 37:20.066
♪ ♪

37:20.066 --> 37:22.300
You--you need to be
grounded in who you are.

37:22.300 --> 37:23.600
That's the person
I'm gonna love,

37:23.600 --> 37:25.600
and that's the person
I wanna marry.

37:25.600 --> 37:27.400
- Do I even have a shot at this?

37:27.400 --> 37:32.100
Is there even a chance for us?

37:32.100 --> 37:33.633
- Coming up...

37:33.633 --> 37:35.500
- Kathryn, I did not know
