37:44.633 --> 37:51.633
♪ ♪

37:55.233 --> 37:57.500
- Hello?

37:57.500 --> 38:00.233
- Holy--[soft laugh]--moly.

38:00.233 --> 38:02.367
- Hi.
Lucy!

38:02.367 --> 38:04.200
You're a little cone-head.

38:04.200 --> 38:07.233
- I am so excited that you
are actually alive right now.

38:07.233 --> 38:08.233
I can't even tell you.
- I am alive.

38:08.233 --> 38:09.600
And I'm well.

38:09.600 --> 38:11.500
- Oh, my God, don't ever
do this to me again,

38:11.500 --> 38:13.767
ever, ever.

38:13.767 --> 38:15.633
- Never again.
- No, I'm serious.

38:15.633 --> 38:17.266
- No, I know.

38:17.266 --> 38:20.000
- Lucy just got spayed,
so she's...

38:20.000 --> 38:21.667
She's a little out of it.
- It's okay.

38:21.667 --> 38:24.000
Some people need these too.
[soft laugh]

38:24.000 --> 38:26.400
- So where the heck
have you been?

38:26.400 --> 38:28.133
And why didn't you
respond to me?

38:28.133 --> 38:29.633
- Well...

38:29.633 --> 38:32.400
- And why did you almost
give me a heart aneurysm?

38:32.400 --> 38:34.533
- [sighs]
I don't know, um.

38:34.533 --> 38:37.000
It's really difficult
to explain.

38:37.000 --> 38:39.233
With everything going on, like,

38:39.233 --> 38:41.266
the Ashley stuff,

38:41.266 --> 38:42.600
it's just been a lot,
and I feel like

38:42.600 --> 38:45.367
I literally just, like,
took a mental break,

38:45.367 --> 38:48.500
and, like, shut my phone off,
locked myself in my apartment,

38:48.500 --> 38:50.000
and just like...

38:50.000 --> 38:51.533
- No, and I get it.
- I don't know.

38:51.533 --> 38:53.433
- But when you have people
that are close to you

38:53.433 --> 38:56.500
that are genuinely concerned
about your well-being...

38:56.500 --> 38:58.000
- It wasn't, like, intentional.

38:58.000 --> 38:59.533
I didn't see your messages.

38:59.533 --> 39:02.433
I didn't see anyone's messages
until... two days ago.

39:02.433 --> 39:05.567
- Which was a week.

39:05.567 --> 39:08.000
- But nothing actually went on.

39:08.000 --> 39:09.433
I literally just
shut off the world.

39:09.433 --> 39:11.266
- Kathryn.

39:11.266 --> 39:14.433
I swear to God, I did not know
if you were alive.

39:14.433 --> 39:16.166
- What?
- Like...

39:16.166 --> 39:18.033
And it--it scared me to death.

39:18.033 --> 39:19.300
It scared me to death.

39:19.300 --> 39:21.433
[soft dramatic music]

39:21.433 --> 39:24.100
- It makes me feel weird
that, like, everyone was like,

39:24.100 --> 39:25.667
"Is she dead or something?"
Like...

39:25.667 --> 39:27.567
- Because you--
- That's just a lot for me.

39:27.567 --> 39:28.700
- Kathryn, that's not normal.

39:28.700 --> 39:30.033
- I know, I know, but, like,

39:30.033 --> 39:31.400
you have to understand, like,

39:31.400 --> 39:33.700
it--it's difficult
to explain to people that

39:33.700 --> 39:37.600
maybe don't deal with
depression, but it's...

39:37.600 --> 39:43.200
♪ ♪

39:43.200 --> 39:45.567
This has all been, like,
the one thing I haven't really,

39:45.567 --> 39:46.700
like, opened up about.

39:46.700 --> 39:51.533
But I have been on meds

39:51.533 --> 39:53.200
for a while now

39:53.200 --> 39:55.066
in dealing with,
like, depression.

39:55.066 --> 39:57.467
And as far as, like,

39:57.467 --> 39:59.467
living sober and,
like, being happy that way,

39:59.467 --> 40:02.200
I've been doing well;
I've got a job now.

40:02.200 --> 40:05.066
I thought to myself,
"I don't need these."

40:05.066 --> 40:07.467
So I just stopped taking them,

40:07.467 --> 40:09.734
and I didn't really realize,
like,

40:09.734 --> 40:11.600
how...
- It would affect...

40:11.600 --> 40:13.166
- It would affect me.
- Your psyche.

40:13.166 --> 40:14.300
- And it really did.
- Yeah.

40:14.300 --> 40:15.767
- It increased my anxiety.

40:15.767 --> 40:18.633
It increased my--
like, emotional, like, response.

40:18.633 --> 40:20.233
And it snowballed.

40:20.233 --> 40:22.500
And...

40:22.500 --> 40:26.734
I've been, in a way,
like, kind of ashamed.

40:26.734 --> 40:28.333
- I don't want you to
ever feel like

40:28.333 --> 40:30.367
you can't come
to me about something.

40:30.367 --> 40:32.500
- I know you wouldn't judge me,
it was just a matter of

40:32.500 --> 40:34.233
like, confronting it--
[sighs]

40:34.233 --> 40:37.200
like, for the first time,
just saying it out loud to you.

40:37.200 --> 40:39.633
When I was in California
and went to rehab,

40:39.633 --> 40:42.066
the official diagnosis was

40:42.066 --> 40:44.066
anxiety and depression.

40:44.066 --> 40:46.633
Getting this diagnosis
gave me some relief

40:46.633 --> 40:49.633
as to why I was choosing

40:49.633 --> 40:53.200
irresponsibly
to numb out those emotions.

40:53.200 --> 40:56.467
That being said,
I now take antidepressants.

40:58.000 --> 41:00.533
- So have you talked to Madison
since you haven't been there?

41:00.533 --> 41:01.633
- Yeah, we're gonna meet

41:01.633 --> 41:04.133
and talk about, like, schedules.

41:04.133 --> 41:06.667
But the thing is,
with her I got really lucky,

41:06.667 --> 41:09.667
because she's a really
good person and a good friend.

41:09.667 --> 41:13.133
And I can open up to her
a little bit more, like,

41:13.133 --> 41:15.400
about, like,
the personal stuff going on.

41:15.400 --> 41:18.533
For a long time, I didn't feel
very deserving of friendships.

41:18.533 --> 41:21.133
You know, I didn't
feel like I had

41:21.133 --> 41:24.266
value to bring
other than a burden.

41:24.266 --> 41:25.667
- No.

41:25.667 --> 41:29.500
I gained so much
from my friendship with you.

41:29.500 --> 41:32.667
Like, I get something
out of our friendship.

41:32.667 --> 41:35.400
There was a moment
where I was so scared

41:35.400 --> 41:39.166
that you weren't responding
to me that I was like,

41:39.166 --> 41:40.567
"What if she's not--"

41:40.567 --> 41:42.533
Like, "What if she's..."
- Oh, my God.

41:42.533 --> 41:44.033
- I love you so much.

41:44.033 --> 41:45.033
[soft groan]
- And you know I love you.

41:45.033 --> 41:46.533
You know I love you.

41:46.533 --> 41:48.166
You're such a good friend to me.

41:48.166 --> 41:49.700
- Don't ever
do that to me again.

41:49.700 --> 41:53.400
- I won't.
I swear, I swear, I swear.

41:53.400 --> 41:56.133
- On the next episode
of "Southern Charm"...

