- [scoffs]

42:01.433 --> 42:03.633
That's so rude.

42:03.633 --> 42:05.567
[playful tone]

42:05.567 --> 42:07.567
- And I asked her one time,
I said, you know,

42:07.567 --> 42:09.033
"What do you see in me?"

